DocomoCss
=========

docomo_css is css in-liner.

DoCoMo(Japanese cell-phone carrier)'s UA cannot use <link rel="stylesheet" /> style css, only can use in-line CSS.

That calls iCSS.


Usage
=====

# app/controllers/articles_controller.rb
class ArticlesController < ApplicationController
  docomo_filter  # please add this
  ...
end

# app/views/articles/index.html.erb
<html>
<head>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'foo', :media => 'handheld, tty' %>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="title">bar</div>
</body>
</html>

# public/stylesheets/foo.css
.title {
  color: red;
}

# result
<html>
<head>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'foo', :media => 'handheld, tty' %>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="title" style="color:red">bar</div>
</body>
</html>


Install
=======

(sudo gem install hpricot)
(sudo gem install milk1000cc-tiny_css --source=http://gems.github.com)
script/plugin install git://github.com/milk1000cc/docomo_css.git


